		<Slide>
			<Caption>
				&lt;p&gt;
Half a cup of cooked carrots is about the same as half a baseball and equals one vegetable serving, or about 25 calories. You can eat even more raw leafy vegetables. Two cups of spinach &amp;mdash; think of two baseballs &amp;mdash; are about 25 calories.&amp;nbsp; 
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Other vegetable servings&lt;/strong&gt; 
